            <p><add hand="#barker">Note of hand. Samuel Perry to Stephen F. Austin &amp; Co.</add></p>
        </div1>
        <div1 type="body">
            

<p>N° 74 due <date when="1817-04-30">30 Apl </date>                                               <placeName>Potosi </placeName><date when="1817-02-26">Feb 26th 1817</date></p>

<p>Sixty days after date I promise to pay to <persName>Stephen F. Austin and Co</persName>
or order Five hundred Dollars without defalcation payable and 
negotiable at the <placeName>Bank of St Louis</placeName> for value Received charged to <persName>S. F.
Austin</persName></p>

<p><persName>Saml. Perry</persName>    [Rubric]</p>

        </div1>
